* [[絲鰭沙鰈|絲鰭沙鰈]] ''S. filipectoralis''
* ''S. hexaradiatus'' {{small|[[Juan_Martín_Díaz_de_Astarloa|Díaz de Astarloa]], [[Romain_Causse|Causse]] & [[Patrice_Pruvost|Pruvost]], 2014}}{{r|Astarloa2014}}
* [[胡氏沙鰈|胡氏沙鰈]] ''S. huysmani'' {{small|[[马克斯·卡尔·威廉·韦伯|Weber]], 1913}}
* [[短頜沙鰈|短頜沙鰈]]（無斑沙鰈）''S. inornatus'' {{small|([[Richard_E._Lloyd|Lloyd]], 1909)}}
* [[日本沙鰈|日本沙鰈]] ''S. japonicus'' {{small|[[Toshiji_Kamohara|Kamohara]], 1936}}
* [[滿月沙鰈|滿月沙鰈]] ''S. latus'' {{small|[[松原喜代松|Matsubara]] & [[Hideo_Takamuki|Takamuki]], 1951}}
* [[醜沙鰈|醜沙鰈]] ''S. leopardus'' {{small|[[Elena_Petrovna_Voronina|Voronina]], 2009}}
* [[長臂沙鰈|長臂沙鰈]] ''S. longimanus'' {{small|[[John_Roxborough_Norman|Norman]], 1927}}
* [[呂宋沙鰈|呂宋沙鰈]] ''S. luzonensis'' {{small|[[Henry_Weed_Fowler|Fowler]], 1934}}
* [[大頜沙鰈|大頜沙鰈]] ''S. macrognathus'' {{small|Fowler, 1934}}
* [[斑沙鰈|斑沙鰈]] ''S. maculatus'' {{small|([[阿尔伯特·甘瑟|Günther]], 1880)}}
* [[多輻沙鰈|多輻沙鰈]] ''S. multiradiatus'' {{small|[[Toshio_Kawai|Kawai]], Amaoka & Séret, 2008}}
* [[新喀里多尼亞沙鰈|新喀里多尼亞沙鰈]] ''S. neocaledonia'' {{small|Kawai, Amaoka & Séret, 2011}}
* [[尼氏沙鰈|尼氏沙鰈]] ''S. nielseni'' {{small|Quéro, Hensley & Maugé, 1989}}
* [[薩氏沙鰈|薩氏沙鰈]] ''S. sunieri'' {{small|Weber & [[Lieven_Ferdinand_de_Beaufort|de Beaufort]], 1929}}
* [[三斑沙鰈|三斑沙鰈]] ''S. triocellatus'' {{small|[[Loren_Paul_Woods|Woods]], 1960}}
* [[高知沙鰈|高知沙鰈]] ''S. xenicus'' {{small|Ochiai & Amaoka, 1962}}
